<text><body>
<lb n="0584b02" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0584b03" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1920 [cf. No. 1921]</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0584b04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"></cb:mulu><note n="0584003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】明曆四年刊宗教大學藏本，【甲】德川時代刊宗教大學藏本</note><cb:jhead>觀心論<note n="0584004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔并序〕－【甲】</note><app n="0584004"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">并序</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note place="inline">亦名煎乳論</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0584b05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0584b06" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Author">天台<note n="0584005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（修禪…述））八字＝（（智者大師說））五字【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0584005"><lem wit="【大】">修禪寺沙門智者述</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">智者大師說</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0584b07" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><p xml:id="pT46p0584b0701">問曰。佛經無量。論亦甚多。弘法之人詵詵蓋
<lb n="0584b08" ed="T"/>世。聽受之眾無處不有。是則法雨普津四眾。
<lb n="0584b09" ed="T"/><note n="0584006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">露＝霑【甲】</note><app n="0584006"><lem wit="【大】">露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">霑</rdg></app>潤利益無邊。何所見聞。更何利益而<note n="0584007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">造斯論＝欲造論也【甲】</note><app n="0584007"><lem wit="【大】">造
<lb n="0584b10" ed="T"/>斯論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">欲造論也</rdg></app>。答曰。如所問言。佛經無量論亦甚多。是
<lb n="0584b11" ed="T"/>事共知。但弘法之人為利物故多施加水之
<lb n="0584b12" ed="T"/>乳。致令聽受之<note n="0584008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＝人【甲】</note><app n="0584008"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">人</rdg></app>失真道味。四眾轉就澆
<lb n="0584b13" ed="T"/><note n="0584009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">離＝漓【甲】</note><app n="0584009"><lem wit="【大】">離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">漓</rdg></app>。致使信心之者漸<note n="0584010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">歇薄談＝漸歇澹【甲】</note><app n="0584010"><lem wit="【大】">歇薄談</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">漸歇澹</rdg></app>。將恐深廣大
<lb n="0584b14" ed="T"/>法不久停留。眾生眼滅失正法利。是以閑生
<lb n="0584b15" ed="T"/>悲傷煩<note n="0584011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">究＝冤【甲】</note><app n="0584011"><lem wit="【大】">究</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">冤</rdg></app>難忍。不惟凡淺寡聞少見。欲<note n="0584012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">助＝眄【甲】</note><app n="0584012"><lem wit="【大】">助</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">眄</rdg></app>
<lb n="0584b16" ed="T"/>鸚鵡。奮其翅力。輒承三寶力。<note n="0584013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欲＝故【甲】</note><app n="0584013"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">故</rdg></app>作斯論也。
<lb n="0584b17" ed="T"/>問者欲知作<note n="0584014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">論＋（意）【甲】</note><app n="0584014"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">論意</rdg></app>者。大意有二。一者自責為諸
<lb n="0584b18" ed="T"/>學徒。二者外諸四眾脫能信受亦可傳之。略
<lb n="0584b19" ed="T"/>以偈答曰。</p>
<lb n="0584b20" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT46p0584b2001"><l>大師將涅槃</l><l>慈父有遺<note n="0584015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">屬＝囑【甲】＊</note><app n="0584015"><lem wit="【大】">屬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囑</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0584b21" ed="T"/><l>四念處修道</l><l><note n="0584016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常＝當【甲】</note><app n="0584016"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">當</rdg></app>依木叉住</l>
<lb n="0584b22" ed="T"/><l>我等非佛子</l><l>不念此遺<app type="star" corresp="#0584015"><lem wit="【大】">屬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囑</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0584b23" ed="T"/><l>乘緩內無道</l><l>戒緩<note n="0584017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">懼＝墮【甲】</note><app n="0584017"><lem wit="【大】">懼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">墮</rdg></app>三途</l>
<lb n="0584b24" ed="T"/><l>由不問觀心</l><l>令他信漸薄</l>
<lb n="0584b25" ed="T"/><l>烏<note n="0584018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鴉＝鵶【甲】＊</note><app n="0584018"><lem wit="【大】">鴉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鵶</rdg></app>不施<note n="0584019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">道＝食【甲】</note><app n="0584019"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">食</rdg></app></l><l>豈報白<app type="star" corresp="#0584018"><lem wit="【大】">鴉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鵶</rdg></app>恩</l>
<lb n="0584b26" ed="T"/><l>非但田不良</l><l>無平等種子</l>
<lb n="0584b27" ed="T"/><l>法雨若不降</l><l>法種必燋枯</l>
<lb n="0584b28" ed="T"/><l>各無來世糧</l><l>失三利致苦</l>
<lb n="0584b29" ed="T"/><l>大法將欲頹</l><l>哀哉見此事</l>
<pb n="0584c" xml:id="T46.1920.0584c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0584c01" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0584c02" ed="T"/><l>平等真法界</l><l>無行<note n="0584020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無能＝亦無【甲】</note><app n="0584020"><lem wit="【大】">無能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">亦無</rdg></app>到</l>
<lb n="0584c03" ed="T"/><l>若能問觀心</l><l>能行亦能到</l>
<lb n="0584c04" ed="T"/><l>即是四念處</l><l>能依木<note n="0584021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">刃＝叉【甲】</note><app n="0584021"><lem wit="【大】">刃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">叉</rdg></app><note n="0584022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">戒＝住【甲】</note><app n="0584022"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">住</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0584c05" ed="T"/><l>乘急內有道</l><l>戒急生人天</l>
<lb n="0584c06" ed="T"/><l>此<note n="0584023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是真佛＝真佛孝【甲】</note><app n="0584023"><lem wit="【大】">是真佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">真佛孝</rdg></app>子</l><l>不乖慈父<app type="star" corresp="#0584015"><lem wit="【大】">屬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囑</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0584c07" ed="T"/><l>天龍皆慶喜</l><l>一切豈不欣</l>
<lb n="0584c08" ed="T"/><l>能報白<app type="star" corresp="#0584018"><lem wit="【大】">鴉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鵶</rdg></app>恩</l><l>普施烏<app type="star" corresp="#0584018"><lem wit="【大】">鴉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鵶</rdg></app>食</l>
<lb n="0584c09" ed="T"/><l>既有好良田</l><l>有平等種子</l>
<lb n="0584c10" ed="T"/><l>法雨應時降</l><l>法種皆生長</l>
<lb n="0584c11" ed="T"/><l>各有未來資</l><l>俱獲三利<note n="0584024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">益＝樂【甲】</note><app n="0584024"><lem wit="【大】">益</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">樂</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0584c12" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0584c13" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>欲聞無上道</l>
<lb n="0584c14" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>聞慧終不發</l>
<lb n="0584c15" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>欲思無上道</l>
<lb n="0584c16" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l><note n="0584025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">恩＝思【甲】</note><app n="0584025"><lem wit="【大】">恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">思</rdg></app>慧終不生</l>
<lb n="0584c17" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>欲修無上道</l>
<lb n="0584c18" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>修慧終不成</l>
<lb n="0584c19" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l><note n="0584026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欲＝勤【甲】</note><app n="0584026"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">勤</rdg></app>修四三昧</l>
<lb n="0584c20" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>困苦無所獲</l>
<lb n="0584c21" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>多聽得言語</l>
<lb n="0584c22" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>未得真實樂</l>
<lb n="0584c23" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>修三昧得定</l>
<lb n="0584c24" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>盲禪無所見</l>
<lb n="0584c25" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>欲懺悔眾罪</l>
<lb n="0584c26" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>罪終難得脫</l>
<lb n="0584c27" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>意欲離煩惱</l>
<lb n="0584c28" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>煩惱終不滅</l>
<lb n="0584c29" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>本<note n="0584027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝欲【甲】</note><app n="0584027"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">欲</rdg></app>利益他</l>
<pb n="0585a" xml:id="T46.1920.0585a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0585a01" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>退轉令他謗</l>
<lb n="0585a02" ed="T"/><l>諸來求法者</l><l>欲興顯佛法</l>
<lb n="0585a03" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>退還大<note n="0585001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＝污【甲】</note><app n="0585001"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">污</rdg></app>損</l>
<lb n="0585a04" ed="T"/><l>如<note n="0585002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝是【甲】</note><app n="0585002"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">是</rdg></app>眾得失</l><l>非偈可具<note n="0585003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陳＝傳【甲】</note><app n="0585003"><lem wit="【大】">陳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">傳</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0585a05" ed="T"/><l>有此諸得失</l><l>無人覺悟者</l>
<lb n="0585a06" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585a07" ed="T"/><l>末<note n="0585004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">代＝世【甲】</note><app n="0585004"><lem wit="【大】">代</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">世</rdg></app>修觀心</l><l>得邪定發見</l>
<lb n="0585a08" ed="T"/><l>辯才無窮盡</l><l>自謂人間寶</l>
<lb n="0585a09" ed="T"/><l>無知者鼻嗅</l><l>野<note n="0585005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">孤＝狐【甲】</note><app n="0585005"><lem wit="【大】">孤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">狐</rdg></app>氣衝眼</l>
<lb n="0585a10" ed="T"/><l>舉尾共<note n="0585006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">脚＝却【甲】</note><app n="0585006"><lem wit="【大】">脚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">却</rdg></app>行</l><l>次第墮坑殞</l>
<lb n="0585a11" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585a12" ed="T"/><l>守鼻隔安般</l><l>及修不淨觀</l>
<lb n="0585a13" ed="T"/><l>安般得四禪</l><l>不免泥梨<note n="0585007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">業＝苦【甲】</note><app n="0585007"><lem wit="【大】">業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">苦</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0585a14" ed="T"/><l>不淨謂無學</l><l>覆鉢受女飯</l>
<lb n="0585a15" ed="T"/><l>設得隨禪生</l><l>墮長壽天難</l>
<lb n="0585a16" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585a17" ed="T"/><l>依事法用心</l><l>無慧發鬼定</l>
<lb n="0585a18" ed="T"/><l>顯異動物心</l><l>事<note n="0585008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">發＝法【甲】＊</note><app n="0585008"><lem wit="【大】">發</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">法</rdg></app>壞佛法</l>
<lb n="0585a19" ed="T"/><l>命終生鬼<note n="0585009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">道＝趣【甲】</note><app n="0585009"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">趣</rdg></app></l><l>九十<note n="0585010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">五＝六【甲】</note><app n="0585010"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">六</rdg></app>眷屬</l>
<lb n="0585a20" ed="T"/><l>像法決疑明</l><l>三師破佛法</l>
<lb n="0585a21" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585a22" ed="T"/><l>內心不為道</l><l>邪諂念名利</l>
<lb n="0585a23" ed="T"/><l>詐現<note n="0585011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">禪坐＝坐禪【甲】＊</note><app n="0585011"><lem wit="【大】">禪坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">坐禪</rdg></app>相</l><l>得名利眷屬</l>
<lb n="0585a24" ed="T"/><l>事<app type="star" corresp="#0585008"><lem wit="【大】">發</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">法</rdg></app>壞他<note n="0585012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＝信【甲】</note><app n="0585012"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">信</rdg></app></l><l>毀損佛正<note n="0585013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＝道【甲】</note><app n="0585013"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">道</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0585a25" ed="T"/><l>此是扇提羅</l><l>死墮無間獄</l>
<lb n="0585a26" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585a27" ed="T"/><l>說<note n="0585014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＝者【甲】</note><app n="0585014"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">者</rdg></app>得解脫</l><l>聽法眾亦然</l>
<lb n="0585a28" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>如貧數他寶</l>
<lb n="0585a29" ed="T"/><l>說者問觀心</l><l>無說則無示</l>
<pb n="0585b" xml:id="T46.1920.0585b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0585b01" ed="T"/><l>聽者問觀心</l><l>無<note n="0585015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">問＝聞【甲】</note><app n="0585015"><lem wit="【大】">問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">聞</rdg></app>亦無得</l>
<lb n="0585b02" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585b03" ed="T"/><l>戒為制心馬</l><l>雖持五部律</l>
<lb n="0585b04" ed="T"/><l>不知問觀心</l><l>心馬終不調</l>
<lb n="0585b05" ed="T"/><l>律住持佛法</l><l>解外不解內</l>
<lb n="0585b06" ed="T"/><l>淨名呵上首</l><l>乃名真奉律</l>
<lb n="0585b07" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585b08" ed="T"/><l>誦經得解脫</l><l>非為世財利</l>
<lb n="0585b09" ed="T"/><l>若能問觀心</l><l>破一微塵中</l>
<lb n="0585b10" ed="T"/><l>出大千經卷</l><l>受持讀誦<note n="0585016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝心【甲】</note><app n="0585016"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">心</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0585b11" ed="T"/><l>聞持無遺忘</l><l>心開得解脫</l>
<lb n="0585b12" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585b13" ed="T"/><l><note n="0585017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觀他＝勸化【甲】</note><app n="0585017"><lem wit="【大】">觀他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">勸化</rdg></app>修供養</l><l>興顯安行人</l>
<lb n="0585b14" ed="T"/><l>密心為自利</l><l><note n="0585018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">猗＝倚【甲】</note><app n="0585018"><lem wit="【大】">猗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">倚</rdg></app>託以資身</l>
<lb n="0585b15" ed="T"/><l>壞他喜捨善</l><l>駝驢以償人</l>
<lb n="0585b16" ed="T"/><l>若能問觀心</l><l>即<note n="0585019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如＝知【甲】</note><app n="0585019"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">知</rdg></app>駝驃也</l>
<lb n="0585b17" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585b18" ed="T"/><l>諸道各有法</l><l>了不自尋研</l>
<lb n="0585b19" ed="T"/><l>忽<note n="0585020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">窺＝闚【甲】＊</note><app n="0585020"><lem wit="【大】">窺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">闚</rdg></app>𨵦釋教</l><l>動經十數年</l>
<lb n="0585b20" ed="T"/><l>非但彼法拙</l><l>亦有謀壞心</l>
<lb n="0585b21" ed="T"/><l>此是迦毘梨</l><l>仙聖豈聽<note n="0585021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">然＝說【甲】</note><app n="0585021"><lem wit="【大】">然</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">說</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0585b22" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585b23" ed="T"/><l>富貴而無道</l><l>多增長憍逸</l>
<lb n="0585b24" ed="T"/><l>若能問觀心</l><l>得真法富貴</l>
<lb n="0585b25" ed="T"/><l>雖高而不危</l><l>雖滿而不溢</l>
<lb n="0585b26" ed="T"/><l>不著世富貴</l><l>心常在道法</l>
<lb n="0585b27" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585b28" ed="T"/><l>貧賤多姦諂</l><l><app type="star" corresp="#0585020"><lem wit="【大】">窺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">闚</rdg></app>𨵦造眾惡</l>
<lb n="0585b29" ed="T"/><l>現被王法治</l><l>死墮三惡道</l>
<pb n="0585c" xml:id="T46.1920.0585c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0585c01" ed="T"/><l>若<note n="0585022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能＝知【甲】</note><app n="0585022"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">知</rdg></app>問觀心</l><l>即安<note n="0585023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">貪＝貧【甲】＊</note><app n="0585023"><lem wit="【大】">貪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">貧</rdg></app>養道</l>
<lb n="0585c02" ed="T"/><l>有道即真貴</l><l>無為即富樂</l>
<lb n="0585c03" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585c04" ed="T"/><l>四眾皆佛子</l><l>無非是法親</l>
<lb n="0585c05" ed="T"/><l>因執善法諍</l><l>遂結未來怨</l>
<lb n="0585c06" ed="T"/><l>若能問觀心</l><l>和合如水乳</l>
<lb n="0585c07" ed="T"/><l>皆師子之子</l><l>悉是旃檀林</l>
<lb n="0585c08" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585c09" ed="T"/><l>年衰身帶<note n="0585024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＝疾【甲】</note><app n="0585024"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">疾</rdg></app></l><l>眼闇耳漸聾</l>
<lb n="0585c10" ed="T"/><l>心昏多忘漏</l><l>年不如一年</l>
<lb n="0585c11" ed="T"/><l>死王金翅鳥</l><l>不久吞命根</l>
<lb n="0585c12" ed="T"/><l>一旦業繩斷</l><l>氣絕豈能言</l>
<lb n="0585c13" ed="T"/><l>為是因緣故</l><l>須造觀心論</l>
<lb n="0585c14" ed="T"/><l>稽首十方佛</l><l>深<note n="0585025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悲＝慈【甲】</note><app n="0585025"><lem wit="【大】">悲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慈</rdg></app>觀心者</l>
<lb n="0585c15" ed="T"/><l>勸善諦觀察</l><l>發正覺妙樂</l>
<lb n="0585c16" ed="T"/><l>稽首十方法</l><l>深悲觀心者</l>
<lb n="0585c17" ed="T"/><l>勸善諦觀察</l><l>得真法免苦</l>
<lb n="0585c18" ed="T"/><l>稽首十方僧</l><l><note n="0585026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若能善觀察∞入大和合海【甲】</note><app n="0585026"><lem wit="【大】">若能善觀察</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">入大和合海</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0585c19" ed="T"/><l><note n="0585027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若能善觀察∞入大和合海【甲】，入大＝大眾ィ【甲】</note><app n="0585027"><lem wit="【大】">入大和合海</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">若能善觀察</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">大眾和合海</rdg></app></l><l>歡喜心無量</l>
<lb n="0585c20" ed="T"/><l>稽首龍樹師</l><l>願加觀心者</l>
<lb n="0585c21" ed="T"/><l>令速得開曉</l><l>亦加捨三心</l>
<lb n="0585c22" ed="T"/><l>今承三寶力</l><l>起三十六問</l>
<lb n="0585c23" ed="T"/><l>其門諸細門</l><l>對事難可數</l>
<lb n="0585c24" ed="T"/><l>若觀一念心</l><l>能答此問者</l>
<lb n="0585c25" ed="T"/><l>當知心眼開</l><l>得入清涼池</l>
<lb n="0585c26" ed="T"/><l>不能答此問</l><l>奈何盲冥也</l>
<lb n="0585c27" ed="T"/><l>少義尚不見</l><l>那得行大道</l>
<lb n="0585c28" ed="T"/><l>哀哉末法中</l><l>無復<note n="0585028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得道者＝行道人【甲】</note><app n="0585028"><lem wit="【大】">得道者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">行道人</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0585c29" ed="T"/><l>設令有三數</l><l>寧別此問也</l>
<pb n="0586a" xml:id="T46.1920.0586a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0586a01" ed="T"/><l>故生悲愍心</l><l>歸命禮三寶</l>
<lb n="0586a02" ed="T"/><l>作此問心論</l><l>令觀者開朗</l>
<lb n="0586a03" ed="T"/><l>願諸見聞者</l><l>莫生疑謗心</l>
<lb n="0586a04" ed="T"/><l>信受勤修習</l><l>必獲大<note n="0586001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利法＝法利【甲】</note><app n="0586001"><lem wit="【大】">利法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">法利</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0586a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT46p0586a0501">問曰。何故作此問<note n="0586002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔觀〕－【甲】</note><app n="0586002"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>心論。答曰。末<note n="0586003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世＝代【甲】</note><app n="0586003"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">代</rdg></app>數寶
<lb n="0586a06" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0585023"><lem wit="【大】">貪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">貧</rdg></app>人本不預此<note n="0586004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＋（論）【甲】</note><app n="0586004"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">言論</rdg></app>若<app type="star" corresp="#0585011"><lem wit="【大】">禪坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">坐禪</rdg></app>觀行之者。但
<lb n="0586a07" ed="T"/><note n="0586005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">安心＝守【甲】</note><app n="0586005"><lem wit="【大】">安心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">守</rdg></app>鼻隔不淨安般。此亦面牆。何可論道。
<lb n="0586a08" ed="T"/>諸有觀心入道得定生<note n="0586006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔倒〕－【甲】</note><app n="0586006"><lem wit="【大】">倒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>解。辯說無窮。自謂
<lb n="0586a09" ed="T"/>人間之寶。豈知邪慢熾然也。今作此問。若句
<lb n="0586a10" ed="T"/>句不知。何得未得謂得未證謂證。法華勸持
<lb n="0586a11" ed="T"/>品。<note n="0586007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0586007"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>說此人難可化<note n="0586008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">度＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0586008"><lem wit="【大】">度</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">度也</rdg></app>。又常不輕品。威音
<lb n="0586a12" ed="T"/>王如來去世之後。如此<note n="0586009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">人＝之【甲】</note><app n="0586009"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">之</rdg></app>類甚多非一。復
<lb n="0586a13" ed="T"/><note n="0586010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＝以【甲】</note><app n="0586010"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以</rdg></app>傷念。一家門徒隨逐積年<note n="0586011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">看＝著【甲】</note><app n="0586011"><lem wit="【大】">看</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>心<note n="0586012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">稍＝積【甲】</note><app n="0586012"><lem wit="【大】">稍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">積</rdg></app>久
<lb n="0586a14" ed="T"/><note n="0586013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔遠〕－【甲】</note><app n="0586013"><lem wit="【大】">遠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。遂不知如此研<note n="0586014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">窮＝竅【甲】</note><app n="0586014"><lem wit="【大】">窮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">竅</rdg></app>問心。是以不染內法。
<lb n="0586a15" ed="T"/>著外文字。偷記<note n="0586015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">注＋（而）【甲】</note><app n="0586015"><lem wit="【大】">注</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">注而</rdg></app>奔走。負經論而浪行。何
<lb n="0586a16" ed="T"/>不<note n="0586016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">施＝絕【甲】</note><app n="0586016"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">絕</rdg></app>語<note n="0586017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0586017"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>置文破一微塵<note n="0586018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">讀＝出【甲】</note><app n="0586018"><lem wit="【大】">讀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">出</rdg></app>大千經卷。念
<lb n="0586a17" ed="T"/>此迷徒隨逐累載。空無所獲。脫一旦冥目誰
<lb n="0586a18" ed="T"/>復示之。以是因緣悲切轉至。故作斯論<note n="0586019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【甲】</note><app n="0586019"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。
<lb n="0586a19" ed="T"/>摩訶般若波羅蜜經明四十二字門。初云。若
<lb n="0586a20" ed="T"/>聞阿字門。即解一切義。所謂一切法初不生
<lb n="0586a21" ed="T"/>也。龍樹<note n="0586020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">并＝菩薩【甲】</note><app n="0586020"><lem wit="【大】">并</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">菩薩</rdg></app>造中論釋摩訶衍<note n="0586021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">論＝經【甲】</note><app n="0586021"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經</rdg></app>。正意以不
<lb n="0586a22" ed="T"/>生等八<note n="0586022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不＝以【甲】</note><app n="0586022"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以</rdg></app>開論端。用一偈釋初不生。云諸法
<lb n="0586a23" ed="T"/>不自生。亦不從他生。不共不無因。是故說無
<lb n="0586a24" ed="T"/>生。今但<note n="0586023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">約＝問【甲】</note><app n="0586023"><lem wit="【大】">約</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">問</rdg></app>觀初自生一句。起三十六問。若
<lb n="0586a25" ed="T"/>於觀心能答此問無滯礙者。當知此行人六
<lb n="0586a26" ed="T"/>種即中入觀<note n="0586024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＋（即）【甲】</note><app n="0586024"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">行即</rdg></app>。五品弟子中即是入初隨喜
<lb n="0586a27" ed="T"/><note n="0586025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔心〕－【甲】</note><app n="0586025"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>位。故<note n="0586026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（法華）＋經【甲】</note><app n="0586026"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">法華經</rdg></app>云。乃至聞一<note n="0586027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">偈＝句【甲】</note><app n="0586027"><lem wit="【大】">偈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">句</rdg></app>。通達無量義。
<lb n="0586a28" ed="T"/>次第如法說。月四月至歲也。論曰。</p>
